    <content>&lt;P&gt;Hello team !&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;We are having the following issue, we have integrated S/4HANA with SAP Task Center + Mobile Start, everything work as expected but, in the Task Center the Notifications of new tasks are not being displayed in the bell in the page header.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;User notifications for taskcenter tasks are not being displayed. When a Purchase Order Approval workflow task is sent to users, the notification is not presented in the workzone.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;The notification is working normally through Fiori's Myinbox.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Only in the workzone that is not working properly.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;The following configurations were made as described in the manual below:&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Receiving SAP S/4HANA Workflow Notifications&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;A href="https://learning.sap.com/learning-journeys/Setting-Up-SAP-Build-Work-Zone-standard-edition-and-SAP-Mobile-Start-with-SAP-S-4HANA/explaining-the-setup-for-sap-s-4hana" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"&gt;https://learning.sap.com/learning-journeys/Setting-Up-SAP-Build-Work-Zone-standard-edition-and-SAP-Mobile-Start-with-SAP-S-4HANA/explaining-the-setup-for-sap-s-4hana&lt;/A&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Enabling Notifications From SAP S/4HANA&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;A href="https://help.sap.com/docs/build-work-zone-standard-edition/sap-build-work-zone-standard-edition/enabling-notifications-from-sap-s-4hana?locale=en-US" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"&gt;https://help.sap.com/docs/build-work-zone-standard-edition/sap-build-work-zone-standard-edition/enabling-notifications-from-sap-s-4hana?locale=en-US&lt;/A&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Enable Notifications for End Users&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;A href="https://help.sap.com/docs/task-center/sap-task-center/enable-notifications-for-end-users" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"&gt;https://help.sap.com/docs/task-center/sap-task-center/enable-notifications-for-end-users&lt;/A&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;When performing