mage-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="juan_gonzalez_7-1731129425784.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/188569iD374FC47E5816CA5/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="juan_gonzalez_7-1731129425784.png" alt="juan_gonzalez_7-1731129425784.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Does anyone have an idea where the error might be or what configuration point I should check?&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Thank you in advance!&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;</content>
