    <content>&lt;P&gt;Hi,&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;I followed the following tutorial on the trial account to publish my Incident Management App created using Business Application Studio, while testing the CAP development, as made from the previous tutorials of this one:&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;A href="https://developers.sap.com/tutorials/deploy-to-cf.html" target="_self" rel="noopener noreferrer"&gt;Deploy to CF&lt;/A&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Everything went as expected, my &lt;STRONG&gt;cf apps&amp;nbsp;&lt;/STRONG&gt;command in then BAS&amp;nbsp; Terminal returning the 2 apps, as in the screenshot of the tutorial, and my &lt;STRONG&gt;cf services&amp;nbsp;&lt;/STRONG&gt; command returns 4 services, because HANA Cloud has been moved from space to subaccount section.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;However, I still do not see my app within the Content Manager of Work Zone, as mentioned in the following tutorial:&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;A href="https://developers.sap.com/tutorials/integrate-with-work-zone.html" target="_self" rel="noopener noreferrer"&gt;Integrate with Work Zone&lt;/A&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;What could be the reason?&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Following are the screenshots of my Role Collections, Subaccount Instances, CF Space and Work Zone Content Manager.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="Assigned Role Collections.png" style="width: 987px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/192412iA5FD9B12053E2890/image-size/large?v=v2&amp;amp;px=999" role="button" title="Assigned Role Collections.png" alt="Assigned Role Collections.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="Content Manager.png" style="width: 999px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/192409i9065DEA4D15248C5/image-size/large?v=v2&amp;amp;px=999" role="button" title="Content Manager.png" alt="Content Manager.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="Instances.png" style="width: 963px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/192408i11DB81FA50E8A3A6/image-size/large?v=v2&amp;amp;px=999" role="button" title="Instances.png" alt="Instances.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="Space.png" style="width: 999px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/192410i44AE7CB21AC8C12A/image-size/large?v=v2&amp;amp;px=999" role="button" title="Space.png" alt="Space.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Thanks in advance.&lt;/P&gt;</content>
